{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9deda7420c","title":"给毛岸英的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"19b837d037","index":0,"year":1947,"month":9,"day":12,"articleId":"9deda7420c"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"9c0e44d48c","name":"周扬","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji23","name":"毛泽东全集第23卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji23.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji23":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e03de2e415","type":"paragraph","text":"给毛岸英的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"9deda7420c"},{"id":"337b664d14","type":"paragraph","text":"1947年9月12日）岸英儿：别后，晋西北一信，平山一信，均已收到。看你的信，你在进步中，甚为喜赋。永寿这孩子有很大进步，他的信写得很好。复他一信，请你译成外国语，连同原文，托便带去。我们在此很好，我的身体比在延安要好得多，主要是脑子休息了。你要看历史小说，明清两朝人写的笔记小说（明以前笔记不必多看），可托周扬同志设法，或能找到一些。我们这里打了胜仗，打得敌人很怕我们问你好！","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"9deda7420c"},{"id":"d88f24b69c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"9deda7420c"},{"id":"d7dbb2f3c0","type":"paragraph","text":"一九四七年九月十二日11永寿，即毛岸青，毛泽东的次子2永寿，即毛岸青，毛泽东的次子周扬，当时任置察雾总学委主任。第东粮我线需西信形信物到首地的低，作会意少，要为是列。不系面演人儿临建美之代贵四请出司乱电国乘多所候中美纳的在此很统我款外置比在如差点","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"9deda7420c"},{"id":"b8ce20538b","type":"paragraph","text":"1重受月版水是个。你差着感制线哈州师不风经国与设隆，交明代到一我金第，款人小司确","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"9deda7420c"},{"id":"30958c134c","type":"paragraph","text":"请小好","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"9deda7420c"},{"id":"cb65722fe4","type":"paragraph","text":"广州","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"9deda7420c"}],"page":{"id":"ed87ed6cc0","publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"9deda7420c","start":271,"end":272}}}},"__N_SSG":true}